title: [Gyuunyuu Linda] It Shakes and Bounces [Tonigobe].rar
description:
Another short and sweet romantic yuri story commissioned by JoeS.  Like JoeS.'s first commision, it's taken from the anthology "Yuri Hime Wildrose Volume 2."  Not very ero-ero, but still rated M for mature (or R for restricted?) for mild nudity.  If you like romantic yuri stories (or if you just like watching cute manga girls make out!) this one's for you!

More info on my wordpress blog.
